query:
SELECT rw.id, rw.latitude, rw.longitude, rw.address, rw.contactName 
FROM routes r 
JOIN route_waypoints rw ON r.id = rw.routeId 
WHERE r.shareToken = '74f21387-337f-4692-83c4-005d5c4638a3' 
ORDER BY rw.id 
LIMIT 5;
